    "description": "Toolkit for styling artifacts with a theme. These artifacts can be slides, docs, reportings, HTML landing pages, etc. There are 10 pre-set themes with colors…",
    "source": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/anthropics/skills/main/skills/theme-factory/SKILL.md",
    "license": "Complete terms in LICENSE.txt",
