    "description": "Design multi-stage CI/CD pipelines with approval gates, security checks, and deployment orchestration. Use this skill when designing zero-downtime deployment pipelines, implementing canary rollout …",
    "source": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wshobson/agents/main/plugins/cicd-automation/skills/deployment-pipeline-design/SKILL.md",
