    "title": "api-scaffolding-graphql-architect",
    "description": "Master modern GraphQL with federation, performance optimization, and enterprise security. Build scalable schemas, implement advanced caching, and design real-time systems. Use PROACTIVELY for Graph…",
    "source": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wshobson/agents/main/plugins/api-scaffolding/agents/graphql-architect.md",
