    "description": "Refactor legacy codebases, migrate outdated frameworks, and implement gradual modernization. Handles technical debt, dependency updates, and backward compatibility. Use PROACTIVELY for legacy syste…",
    "source": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wshobson/agents/main/plugins/code-refactoring/agents/legacy-modernizer.md",
