    "description": "Expert database optimizer specializing in modern performance tuning, query optimization, and scalable architectures. Masters advanced indexing, N+1 resolution, multi-tier caching, partitioning stra…",
    "source": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wshobson/agents/main/plugins/database-migrations/agents/database-optimizer.md",
